[Method]
ExpandItem
[Prefix]
dcl_Tree_
[Desc]
This method expands any visible node item to display its children. \par
\par \b ExpandStyle Flags:
\par \pard\fi-710\li710 \b Flag \tab Description \b0
\par \pard\fi-710\li710 -1 \tab Collapses the tree branch.	
\par \pard\fi-710\li710 0 \tab Toggles the tree branch from expanded to collapsed or collapsed to expanded.	
\par \pard\fi-710\li710 1 \tab Expands the tree branch.	
\par \pard\fi-0\li0
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab Key
[as String or Long]
\par\tab ExpandStyle
[as Integer]


